App to mock API



- User should have the possibility to mock web api
- should have the possibility to add any endpoint and content for GET and POST
- app should notice users for usage of api
- app should sent info to users for succes / fail
- support for many formats - json / html
- possibility to change error status codes / messages
- store of logs for requests + response
- possibillity  to retry callbacks  /based on 
logs